        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 27. Trematooecia hexagonalis (Canu & Bassler, 1930). A–F, USNM 8513, holotype, Galápagos Islands. A, B, groups of zooids. C, close-up of zooids and opercula. D, primary orifice. E, F, ovicelled zooids and small, elliptical frontal avicularia. Scale bars: A = 500 µm; B = 200 µm; C, E, F = 200 µm; D = 100 µm." ;
